{"tha-ap525:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap525:0.2":"Tinadayakavagga ","tha-ap525:0.3":"Saranagamaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap525:1.1":"“Aruhimha tada navam, ","tha-ap525:1.2":"bhikkhu cajiviko caham; ","tha-ap525:1.3":"Navaya bhijjamanaya, ","tha-ap525:1.4":"bhikkhu me saranam ada. ","tha-ap525:2.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap525:2.2":"yam so me saranam ada; ","tha-ap525:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap525:2.4":"saranagamane phalam. ","tha-ap525:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap525:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap525:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap525:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap525:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap525:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap525:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap525:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap525:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap525:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saranagamaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap525:7.1":"Saranagamaniyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}